related_questions.question: How much do Netflix employees get paid?
related_questions.snippet: The average Netflix salary ranges from approximately $28,525 per year for Customer Service Representative to $480,000 per year for Senior User Interface Designer. Average Netflix hourly pay ranges from approximately $10.57 per hour for Operations Associate to $16.20 per hour for Front Desk Manager.

related_questions.question: Does Netflix have entry level jobs?
related_questions.snippet: There are no entry-level jobs at Netflix, so if you have just graduated from college, then most likely you have nothing to do here.

related_questions.snippet: Method 1 Signing Up on the WebVisit www.netflix.com in a web browser. ... Click the “Join Free for a Month” button. ... Click “See the Plans” to view your options. ... Select a streaming plan, then click “Continue.” ... Create a new account. ... Select a payment option. ... Enter your payment details. ... Start your Netflix membership.
